title: Samsung’s Chip Profit Soars in Strong Signal for Global AI Rush
description: Samsung Electronics Co.’s chip unit beat expectations with a more than five-fold profit gain in profit, a healthy signal for an artificial intelligence spending wave that’s triggered a surge in memory demand.
